11100051.text:
[Recommended Level] 12
Hesuth hunter Jimmy Ace
has offered me a chance to hunt a Hesuth.
Why not give it a try?

11100052.text:
[Recommended Level] 16
Did Jimmy Ace really acknowledge me?
I'll start off by hunting a Hesuth.

11100053.text:
[Recommended Level] 16
Anyway, I think there's a Hesuth around here.
I should find it.

11100054.text:
[Recommended Level] 20
I don't know if Jimmy Ace is happy
or sad to see me again.
What kind of Hesuth will I encounter this time? I'd better find out.

11100055.text:
[Recommended Level] 21
I don't know if Krunchi, Munchi, or even Jimmy Ace
are decent hunters,
but I'll focus on hunting a Hesuth for now.

11100056.text:
[Recommended Level] 32
Jimmy Ace must have gone after a Hesuth by himself.
He could be wherever a Hesuth is. I'd better look for any clues.

11100057.text:
[Recommended Level] 43
Jimmy Ace is still nowhere to be found.
I'd better look for any traces of a Hesuth, and for him, too.

11100058.text:
[Recommended Level] 48
Krunchi is desperate to find Jimmy Ace.
I'd better look for any traces of a Hesuth, and for him, too.

11100059.text:
[Recommended Level] 52
Munchi suggested we form our own expedition team.
What about Jimmy Ace and Krunchi?
For now, I should try to find this incredible Hesuth.

11100060.text:
[Recommended Level] 54
The future of the Hesuth Expedition rests on my shoulders.
All right, then I'll take care of it!
I should go hunt this Hesuth.

11100061.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
Jimmy Ace doesn't seem to recognize me at all.
I should find and hunt a Hesuth for now.

11100062.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
Krunchi has been betrayed by Munchi.
I should hunt a Hesuth for him so he can see that not everyone has abandoned him.

11100063.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
Krunchi is struggling
to keep the promise he made to the others.
I should hunt more Hesuths and help him.

11100064.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
Jimmy Ace said he'd prepare a perfect Hesuth for me.
I should find it and hunt it.

11100065.text:
[Recommended Level] 60
What is he talking about? When did I ever run away?
I'd better find and hunt a Hesuth to prove him wrong.

11100066.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
I defeated a Hesuth, but Jimmy Ace didn't disappear.
I should talk to him and see if he recognizes me.

11100067.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
Krunchi seems emotional since he found Jimmy Ace.
I should keep an eye on them as a new recruit of the Hesuth Expedition.

11100068.text:
[Recommended Level] 12
Jimmy Ace and the others are shouting something on the Bottomless Pit Trail.
They're looking for someone to hunt Hesuths with.
I should talk to them.

11100069.text:
[Recommended Level] 16
Jimmy Ace, Krunchi, and Munchi are recruiting Hesuth hunters
near the Rocky Hill.
I should talk to them.

11100070.text:
[Recommended Level] 16
A Hesuth has shown up near the Highland Central Trail.
I'd better find the Hesuth hunters, Jimmy Ace, Krunchi, and Munchi, and talk to them.

11100071.text:
[Recommended Level] 20
The Hesuth hunters Jimmy Ace, Krunchi, and Munchi, have shown up near the Bottomless Pit.
I'd better go look for Hesuth traces with them.

11100072.text:
[Recommended Level] 21
I hear familiar voices coming from the Destroyed Ploggle Village.
They're voices of the Hesuth hunters Jimmy Ace, Krunchi, and Munchi.
I should talk to them.

11100073.text:
[Recommended Level] 32
Krunchi and Munchi are looking for Jimmy Ace on the Cobweb Forest Trail.
What are the Sapphire Basin's Hesuth hunters doing in the Taero Forest?
I'd better ask.

11100074.text:
[Recommended Level] 43
Krunchi and Munchi must be on the south side of the Shadowed Mistwood.
Where's Jimmy Ace?
I should ask.

11100075.text:
[Recommended Level] 48
Krunchi and Munchi have shown up at the Nepenthes Marsh!
Did something bad really happen to Jimmy Ace?
I'd better ask.

11100076.text:
[Recommended Level] 52
Munchi is alone at Sunrise Climb.
Did something happen between him and Krunchi?
I'd better ask.

11100077.text:
[Recommended Level] 54
Krunchi and Munchi are bickering on North Swamp Coastal Way.
The Hesuth Expedition is not going to last at this rate...
I'd better talk to them.

11100078.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
Jimmy Ace, who disappeared from the Taero Forest, has resurfaced in the Caelite Land.
I'd better go to the Ivory Gale Haewol Quarters and talk to him.

11100079.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
He's recruiting Hesuth hunters on Specter Hill.
I should talk to him.

11100080.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
Krunchi has shown up in the Dreamy Forest.
What is it this time?
I'd better ask.

11100081.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
The Hesuth Expedition has shown up in a quiet corner of Dragonhead Cape.
Is it Jimmy Ace and Chuah or Krunchi?
I'd better find out.

11100082.text:
[Recommended Level] 60
The Hesuth Expedition has shown up at the Hideout of Disaster.
Did Krunchi pay off his debt?
I'd better ask.

11100083.text:
[Recommended Level] 51
I defeated a Hesuth, but Jimmy Ace didn't disappear.
I should talk to him and find out what he's waiting for.

11100084.text:
[Recommended Level] 56
Finally Krunchi has met up with Jimmy Ace.
Did the Hesuth hunt bring them together?
I should talk to them.

11100085.text: [Recommended level] 63\nA seawater hunter has appeared at the Black Dawn outpost!

11100086.text: [Recommended level] 63\nSeawater hunters who have found another seawater in the Sea Dragon Mountains!\nI'll show you my skills this time too!

11100088.text:
[Recommended level] 62
A seawater hunter has appeared in the Sea Dragon Mountains!
How did you get to this barren place? 
You mean you came all the way here to hunt seawater?

11100089.text: [Recommended level] 62\nHarvard God has entrusted you with a seawater hunting mission.\nBut you have to hold your breath?

11100092.text: [Recommended level] 67 \nJi-Geun Woo, who secretly told me to come alone.

11100094.text: [Recommended level] 73\nSeawater hunters Harvest God and Ododog appeared on the polluted land!\nWhat happened to Ji-geun Woo?

11100095.text: [Recommended Level] 73\nWoo Ji-geun, who was in a team with the Black Dawn! \nYou said you stole seawater and dedicated it to the Black Dawn?

11100097.text: [Recommended level] 73\nDodok Oh, a seawater hunter, sent a message asking him to come to the Black Dawn camp.

11100098.text: [Recommended level] 73\nLet's show off our skills this time to prevent the Black Dawn from taking over the seawater! \nHaesu! Come on!
